               <msContents>
                  <summary>Fragments of the Homilies of St.
                            Michael, and Other Texts<p>The rubrics and thus the titles of most texts are faded and
                                illegible. The text is fragmented and the individual elements do not
                                follow the normal sequence. </p>
                     <p> The manuscript is severely
                                damaged after fol. 82v and identifying the texts is difficult; there
                                are however sections (e.g. a Synaxarium entry) pertaining to the
                                month of Maskaram.</p>
                     
                  </summary>
